<h4><a href="https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1038015.htm">三星是全球第二大移动端相机制造商</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370638" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/samsung_galaxy_zflip_9411.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/samsung_galaxy_zflip_9411.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/samsung_galaxy_zflip_9411-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/samsung_galaxy_zflip_9411-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/samsung_galaxy_zflip_9411-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>cnBeta 消息，市场调查机构 Strategy Analytics 最新报告指，三星是仅次于索尼的全球第二大移动端相机制造商。2020 年上半年，三星在移动相机传感器市场的营收占比为 32%，索尼的市场份额为 44%，中国图像传感器公司 OmniVision 的收入份额为 9％。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.jiemian.com/article/5084583.html">黄峥：拼多多要在农业领域做重投入和创新</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370639" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wmYPkb8W3o-1dbT_dDassBWbLtxZbgxl9o3oX_aN6F8.jpeg" alt="" width="1200" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wmYPkb8W3o-1dbT_dDassBWbLtxZbgxl9o3oX_aN6F8.jpeg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wmYPkb8W3o-1dbT_dDassBWbLtxZbgxl9o3oX_aN6F8-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wmYPkb8W3o-1dbT_dDassBWbLtxZbgxl9o3oX_aN6F8-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wmYPkb8W3o-1dbT_dDassBWbLtxZbgxl9o3oX_aN6F8-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>《科创板日报》消息，拼多多董事长黄峥在内部周年庆祝活动上表示，「5 岁的拼多多已经成为一家全社会的公司，肩负着巨大的社会责任」。</p>
<p>黄峥强调，拼多多要在农业领域继续做大量重投入和深度创新。对于未来，黄峥表示拼多多全员都要「开启硬核奋斗模式」。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1038035.htm">Digitimes 预测智能手机出货量实现两位数增长</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370640" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5e68fc4d54f25c381d11733a.jpeg" alt="" width="1136" height="852" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5e68fc4d54f25c381d11733a.jpeg 1136w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5e68fc4d54f25c381d11733a-360x270.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5e68fc4d54f25c381d11733a-768x576.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5e68fc4d54f25c381d11733a-1024x768.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1136px) 100vw, 1136px" /></p>
<p>快科技消息，DigiTimes Research 报告指出，在连续三年下降之后，预计 2021 年全球智能手机出货量将实现两位数增长。该报告称，来年的出货量可能增长 1.5 亿部，这主要是由于 5G 在美国，西欧和日本等地区的运营加速。</p>
<p>此外，报告预测三星和苹果在出货量上将分别获全球第一和第二，OPPO、vivo 以及小米则将分别位列 3-5 名。</p>
<h4><a href="https://9to5mac.com/2020/10/08/iphone-for-life/">苹果申请「iPhone for Life」商标</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370641" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone-for-Life-alongside-iPhone-Upgrade-Program.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="512" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone-for-Life-alongside-iPhone-Upgrade-Program.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone-for-Life-alongside-iPhone-Upgrade-Program-360x180.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone-for-Life-alongside-iPhone-Upgrade-Program-768x384.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>9to5mac 消息，苹果于 2020 年 4 月在香港地区申请了「iPhone for Life」商标。报道指，相同商标美国市场虽然没有，但在其它市场曾出现，主要被运营商和苹果门店用于「iPhone Upgrade Program」的项目。</p>
